Happy Holidays from our family to yours ❤️🎄🎅🏾

My great grandparents have departed months apart from one another 🕊️🕊️ 100 years old and have been married for almost 80 years . I love these two so much words can’t describe man. The amount of love they gave my siblings and I was unconditional. My great grandfather was a powerful man. A people person. Every room he went in you would know he was there. My great grand mother was calm beautiful never said to much unless she was comfortable with you. Complete opposites. But madly in love. The fact that my grand father was an orphan and created so much legacy is truly amazing. Growing up I did not like my name pop pop, but I carry it being Lawrence H Robinson 4th because it’s yours. I love you two and may you both keep loving on each other in heaven. A true love story I got to witness The Robinsons ❤️🙏🏾

Happy birthday to my baby 😍 I love you so much beautiful and they way you take care of the kids makes me love you even more. You didn’t want to leave our baby girl and go on vacation so I brought vacation and all the vibes to you ❤️ I love spoiling you….
